      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I've taken care of it, and it's ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
