    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a mechanically sound example of the E46 chassis, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The vehicle has received proactive maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. The suspension maintains its factory-spec handling characteristics with refreshed bushings, ensuring the chassis stays composed under high lateral loads. A driver-focused machine with a clean valvetrain and consistent compression across all cylinders.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
