    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i in Alpine White over a Mocha Dakota leather interior. This vehicle has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and reflects the pride of ownership. The exterior paint retains a brilliant shine with only a few minor stone chips on the front valence, consistent with light highway use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and exceptionally clean; the leather bolsters are firm, and the fine-line oak wood trim is free of scratches. All premium features, including the panoramic moonroof, Harman Kardon surround sound, and heated seats, are in perfect working order. Mechanically, this SUV is turn-key. It comes with a comprehensive service folder documenting every oil change and inspection performed at the dealership. We recently replaced the cabin air filters and performed a four-wheel alignment. The tires are matching Pirellis with approximately 70% tread remaining. It delivers a smooth, powerful ride with no warning lights or deferred maintenance. This is a solid, honest example of a luxury classic, perfect for a buyer who prioritizes a documented history and a vehicle that has been treated with respect.",
